      <title>在美国关键通胀数据出现之前，黄金保持创纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者关注美国通胀数据，黄金价格创下历史新高，这可能有助于塑造美联储的利率前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</guid>
